group_1.narration: The I Tracer is a type of nanomachine@that attaches itself to the brain left in a@Mahou Shoujo's body and hacks their thoughts.
Negative emotions,@such as hatred and anger,@are directed to the act of "fighting".
Their hatred of fighting@anger towards conflict@makes them want to eliminate it,@transforming them into the ultimate pacifists.
The reason I feel so awful
is because of all this fighting.
I call it...@THE ALL MAHOU SHOUJO@IROHAFICATION PROJECT!
